
JOUR652: Midterm
Part 1: Q&A

Directions:
1. Use a text editor (like Notepad if you're on a PC, or TextEdit if you're on a
Mac, or even a code editor like Brackets) to complete this assignment.
2. This assignment is open book.
3. Answer every question. There are 15 questions total.
4. If you don't understand what I'm asking for on a question, please ask me.
5. When you are done, please save your document as “your-name-midterm-pt1.txt” and
submit on ELMS as a file upload. (Do not upload this to your repo.)
